  <brief_title>Study of FFI-1010 in Pediatric Kidney Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Safety and Usability Evaluation Study of FFI-1010 Single Administration for Children Under 18 Years Old With Kidney Disease (Phase III Study).</official_title>
